      <div class="opps-dashboard">
        <div class="opps-grid">
          <div class="opp-card" style="--opp-color: var(--yellow, #ffdb00)">
            <div class="opp-card__header">
              <span class="opp-card__count">14</span>
              <h3 class="opp-card__title">Unified Customer Information</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="opp-card__desc">Co-workers switch between 5+ systems per call. No single view of the customer exists.</p>
            <p class="opp-card__example">One place for all customer and order information: profiles, history, notes, cases.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="opp-card" style="--opp-color: #5aaaff">
            <div class="opp-card__header">
              <span class="opp-card__count">12</span>
              <h3 class="opp-card__title">Automation &amp; AI</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="opp-card__desc">After-call work takes minutes per call. Summaries, notes, and status changes are all manual.</p>
            <p class="opp-card__example">AI-generated call summaries, auto-filled fields, smart templates that learn from patterns.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="opp-card" style="--opp-color: #3ee0a5">
            <div class="opp-card__header">
              <span class="opp-card__count">10</span>
              <h3 class="opp-card__title">Knowledge &amp; Documentation</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="opp-card__desc">VETA procedures change constantly. Co-workers can't find the right one during a live call.</p>
            <p class="opp-card__example">Trustworthy, searchable knowledge base embedded directly in the workflow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="opp-card" style="--opp-color: #ff9f43">
            <div class="opp-card__header">
              <span class="opp-card__count">10</span>
              <h3 class="opp-card__title">Process Standardisation</h3>
